description: Primes p such that 94 is not a square mod p.
links: Vincenzo Librandi, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1000
prog: (MAGMA) [p: p in PrimesUpTo(443) | not IsSquare(R! 94) where R:= ResidueClassRing(p)]; // _Vincenzo Librandi_, Sep 10 2012(MAGMA) [p: p in PrimesInInterval(3,443) | JacobiSymbol(94,p) eq -1]; // _Bruno Berselli_, Sep 10 2012
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
extensions: Offset changed from 0 to 1 by _Vincenzo Librandi_, Sep 10 2012
